name: Return(for Global game jam 2019)
description:
You wake up in a strange and foreign hellscape, attacking your sanity with its nightmarish disregard for logic. Where are you? And where is home? Navigate your way through a weird world and uncover secrets in this "choose-your-own-nightmare" text game.

Credits:

Myself - Writing and coding in Twine

Alex - Art assets done in photoshop
